draws its sharp claws into its paws to slinkily sneak about without making any incriminating footsteps. For some reason, this POK\u00e9MON loves shiny coins that glitter with light."},{"version":"emerald","text":"MEOWTH withdraw their sharp claws into their paws to silently sneak about. For some reason, this POK\u00e9MON loves shiny coins that glitter with light."},{"version":"firered","text":"All it does is sleep during the daytime. At night, it patrols its territory with its eyes aglow."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Adores round objects. It wanders the streets on a nightly basis to look for dropped loose change."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It is nocturnal in nature. If it spots something shiny, its eyes glitter brightly."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It is nocturnal in nature. If it spots something shiny, its eyes glitter brightly."},{"version":"platinum","text":"It is nocturnal in nature. If it spots something shiny, its eyes glitter brightly."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"It is fascinated by round objects. It can\u2019t stop playing with them until it tires and falls asleep."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It loves anything that shines. It especially adores coins that it picks up and secretly hoards."},{"version":"black","text":"It is nocturnal in nature. If it spots something shiny, its eyes glitter brightly."},{"version":"white","text":"It is nocturnal in nature. If it spots something shiny, its eyes glitter brightly."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It is nocturnal in nature. If it spots something shiny, its eyes glitter brightly."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It is nocturnal in nature. If it spots something shiny, its eyes glitter brightly."},{"version":"x","text":"It is nocturnal in nature. If it spots something shiny, its eyes glitter brightly."},{"version":"y","text":"Adores round objects. It wanders the streets on a nightly basis to look for dropped loose change."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Meowth withdraws its sharp claws into its paws to slinkily sneak about without making any incriminating footsteps. For some reason, this Pok\u00e9mon loves shiny coins that glitter with light."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Meowth withdraws its sharp claws into its paws to slinkily sneak about without making any incriminating footsteps. For some reason, this Pok\u00e9mon loves shiny coins that glitter with light."},{"version":"sun","text":"It lies around all day, becoming active near dusk. At night, it wanders the city in search of loose change."},{"version":"moon","text":"It loves shiny things. It often fights with Murkrow over prey they\u2019re both trying to catch."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"When visiting a junkyard, you may catch sight of it having an intense fight with Murkrow over shiny objects."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It loves coins, so if you give it one, you can make friends with Meowth easily. But it\u2019s fickle, so you can\u2019t count on that friendship lasting."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Appears to be more active at night. It loves round and shiny things. It can\u2019t stop itself from picking them up."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Appears to be more active at night. It loves round and shiny things. It can\u2019t stop itself from picking them up."},{"version":"sword","text":"It loves to collect shiny things. If it\u2019s in a good mood, it might even let its Trainer have a look at its hoard of treasures."}],"evo":{"name":"meowth","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"persian","level":1,"min_level":28,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_u